name: BetaPro Equal Weight Canadian Bank 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: ATMU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions, and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of the Solactive Equal Weight Canada Banks Index. ATMU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
